;;;42     
;;;43     static inline void cpu_asl(CpuAdrMode adrmode)   
000000  e92d5ff0          PUSH     {r4-r12,lr}
;;;44     {   
000004  4682              MOV      r10,r0
;;;45     	uint16_t savepc = /*opcodetable[opcode].*/adrmode();

                          AREA ||i.cpu_brk||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  cpu_brk PROC
;;;147    
;;;148    static inline void cpu_brk(CpuAdrMode adrmode)   
000000  b510              PUSH     {r4,lr}
;;;149    {   
000002  4601              MOV      r1,r0
;;;150    	PC++; 
000004  4817              LDR      r0,|L17.100|
000006  8800              LDRH     r0,[r0,#0]  ; PC
000008  1c40              ADDS     r0,r0,#1
00000a  4a16              LDR      r2,|L17.100|
00000c  8010              STRH     r0,[r2,#0]
;;;151    
;;;152    	// cpu_putmemory(0x0100+S--,(uint8_t)(PC>>8));   
;;;153    	// cpu_putmemory(0x0100+S--,(uint8_t)(PC & 0xff));   
;;;154    	// cpu_putmemory(0x0100+S--,P);  
;;;155    	cpu_push16stack(PC);
00000e  8810              LDRH     r0,[r2,#0]  ; PC
000010  4a15              LDR      r2,|L17.104|
000012  7812              LDRB     r2,[r2,#0]  ; S
000014  1e92              SUBS     r2,r2,#2
000016  4b14              LDR      r3,|L17.104|
000018  701a              STRB     r2,[r3,#0]
00001a  461a              MOV      r2,r3
00001c  7812              LDRB     r2,[r2,#0]  ; S
00001e  f2021201          ADD      r2,r2,#0x101
000022  4b12              LDR      r3,|L17.108|
000024  5298              STRH     r0,[r3,r2]
000026  bf00              NOP      
;;;156    	cpu_pushstack(P);
000028  4a11              LDR      r2,|L17.112|
00002a  7810              LDRB     r0,[r2,#0]  ; P
00002c  4a0e              LDR      r2,|L17.104|
00002e  7812              LDRB     r2,[r2,#0]  ; S
000030  4b0d              LDR      r3,|L17.104|
000032  781b              LDRB     r3,[r3,#0]  ; S
000034  1e5b              SUBS     r3,r3,#1
000036  4c0c              LDR      r4,|L17.104|
000038  7023              STRB     r3,[r4,#0]
00003a  f5027280          ADD      r2,r2,#0x100
00003e  4b0b              LDR      r3,|L17.108|
000040  5498              STRB     r0,[r3,r2]
000042  bf00              NOP      
;;;157    
;;;158    	P |= 0x14;     
000044  480a              LDR      r0,|L17.112|
000046  7800              LDRB     r0,[r0,#0]  ; P
000048  f0400014          ORR      r0,r0,#0x14
00004c  4a08              LDR      r2,|L17.112|
00004e  7010              STRB     r0,[r2,#0]
;;;159    
;;;160    	// PC = cpu_getmemory16(0xfffe);
;;;161    	PC = IRQ_VECTOR;
000050  4808              LDR      r0,|L17.116|
000052  6800              LDR      r0,[r0,#0]  ; prg_rombank1
000054  f5005040          ADD      r0,r0,#0x3000
000058  f8b00ffe          LDRH     r0,[r0,#0xffe]
00005c  4a01              LDR      r2,|L17.100|
00005e  8010              STRH     r0,[r2,#0]
;;;162    	// PC=cpu_getmemory(0xfffe);   
;;;163    	// PC |= cpu_getmemory(0xffff) << 8;    
;;;164    }   
000060  bd10              POP      {r4,pc}
;;;165    
                          ENDP

                  cpu_indx PROC
;;;113    /* (ZP,X) */   
;;;114    static inline uint16_t cpu_indx(void)   
000000  bf00              NOP      
000002  4808              LDR      r0,|L43.36|
000004  8800              LDRH     r0,[r0,#0]  ; PC
000006  1c40              ADDS     r0,r0,#1
000008  4b06              LDR      r3,|L43.36|
00000a  8018              STRH     r0,[r3,#0]
00000c  4806              LDR      r0,|L43.40|
00000e  7800              LDRB     r0,[r0,#0]  ; operand
;;;115    {      
;;;116    	uint16_t savepc;

                  cpu_irq PROC
;;;150    /* Maskerable Interrupt */   
;;;151    void cpu_irq(void)   
000000  4915              LDR      r1,|L47.88|
;;;152    {   
;;;153    	// cpu_putmemory(0x0100+S--,(uint8_t)(PC>>8));   
;;;154    	// cpu_putmemory(0x0100+S--,(uint8_t)(PC & 0xff));   
;;;155    	// cpu_putmemory(0x0100+S--,P);  
;;;156    	cpu_push16stack(PC);
000002  8808              LDRH     r0,[r1,#0]  ; PC
000004  4915              LDR      r1,|L47.92|
000006  7809              LDRB     r1,[r1,#0]  ; S
000008  1e89              SUBS     r1,r1,#2
00000a  4a14              LDR      r2,|L47.92|
00000c  7011              STRB     r1,[r2,#0]
00000e  4611              MOV      r1,r2
000010  7809              LDRB     r1,[r1,#0]  ; S
000012  f2011101          ADD      r1,r1,#0x101
000016  4a12              LDR      r2,|L47.96|
000018  5250              STRH     r0,[r2,r1]
00001a  bf00              NOP      
;;;157    	cpu_pushstack(P);
00001c  4911              LDR      r1,|L47.100|
00001e  7808              LDRB     r0,[r1,#0]  ; P
000020  490e              LDR      r1,|L47.92|
000022  7809              LDRB     r1,[r1,#0]  ; S
000024  4a0d              LDR      r2,|L47.92|
000026  7812              LDRB     r2,[r2,#0]  ; S
000028  1e52              SUBS     r2,r2,#1
00002a  4b0c              LDR      r3,|L47.92|
00002c  701a              STRB     r2,[r3,#0]
00002e  f5017180          ADD      r1,r1,#0x100
000032  4a0b              LDR      r2,|L47.96|
000034  5450              STRB     r0,[r2,r1]
000036  bf00              NOP      
;;;158    
;;;159    	P |= 0x04;     
000038  480a              LDR      r0,|L47.100|
00003a  7800              LDRB     r0,[r0,#0]  ; P
00003c  f0400004          ORR      r0,r0,#4
000040  4908              LDR      r1,|L47.100|

;;;361    /* set negative flag if bit 8 set??? can this happen on an LSR? */

                  cpu_nmi PROC
;;;133    /* Non maskerable interrupt */   
;;;134    void cpu_nmi(void)   
000000  4915              LDR      r1,|L63.88|
;;;135    {   
;;;136    	// cpu_putmemory(0x0100+S--,(uint8_t)(PC>>8));   
;;;137    	// cpu_putmemory(0x0100+S--,(uint8_t)(PC & 0xff));   
;;;138    	// cpu_putmemory(0x0100+S--,P);   
;;;139    	cpu_push16stack(PC);
000002  8808              LDRH     r0,[r1,#0]  ; PC
000004  4915              LDR      r1,|L63.92|
000006  7809              LDRB     r1,[r1,#0]  ; S
000008  1e89              SUBS     r1,r1,#2
00000a  4a14              LDR      r2,|L63.92|
00000c  7011              STRB     r1,[r2,#0]
00000e  4611              MOV      r1,r2
000010  7809              LDRB     r1,[r1,#0]  ; S
000012  f2011101          ADD      r1,r1,#0x101
000016  4a12              LDR      r2,|L63.96|
000018  5250              STRH     r0,[r2,r1]
00001a  bf00              NOP      
;;;140    	cpu_pushstack(P);
00001c  4911              LDR      r1,|L63.100|
00001e  7808              LDRB     r0,[r1,#0]  ; P
000020  490e              LDR      r1,|L63.92|
000022  7809              LDRB     r1,[r1,#0]  ; S
000024  4a0d              LDR      r2,|L63.92|
000026  7812              LDRB     r2,[r2,#0]  ; S
000028  1e52              SUBS     r2,r2,#1
00002a  4b0c              LDR      r3,|L63.92|
00002c  701a              STRB     r2,[r3,#0]
00002e  f5017180          ADD      r1,r1,#0x100
000032  4a0b              LDR      r2,|L63.96|
000034  5450              STRB     r0,[r2,r1]
000036  bf00              NOP      
;;;141    
;;;142    	P |= 0x04; 
000038  480a              LDR      r0,|L63.100|
00003a  7800              LDRB     r0,[r0,#0]  ; P
00003c  f0400004          ORR      r0,r0,#4
000040  4908              LDR      r1,|L63.100|
000042  7008              STRB     r0,[r1,#0]
;;;143    
;;;144    	// PC = cpu_getmemory16(0xfffa);
;;;145    	PC = NMI_VECTOR;
000044  4808              LDR      r0,|L63.104|
000046  6800              LDR      r0,[r0,#0]  ; prg_rombank1
000048  f5005040          ADD      r0,r0,#0x3000
00004c  f8b00ffa          LDRH     r0,[r0,#0xffa]
000050  4901              LDR      r1,|L63.88|
000052  8008              STRH     r0,[r1,#0]
;;;146    	// PC=cpu_getmemory(0xfffa);   
;;;147    	// PC |= cpu_getmemory(0xfffb) << 8;   
;;;148    }   
000054  4770              BX       lr
;;;149    
                          ENDP

000056  0000              DCW      0x0000
                  |L63.88|

                  cpu_relative PROC
;;;28     /* Branch */   
;;;29     static inline uint16_t cpu_relative(void)   
000000  bf00              NOP      
000002  490d              LDR      r1,|L71.56|
000004  8809              LDRH     r1,[r1,#0]  ; PC
000006  1c49              ADDS     r1,r1,#1
000008  4a0b              LDR      r2,|L71.56|
00000a  8011              STRH     r1,[r2,#0]
00000c  490b              LDR      r1,|L71.60|
00000e  7809              LDRB     r1,[r1,#0]  ; operand
;;;30     {     
;;;31     	uint16_t savepc;
;;;32       	savepc  = cpu_getoperand();  
000010  4608              MOV      r0,r1
;;;33     
;;;34       	if (savepc & 0x80) savepc -= 0x100;   
000012  f0000180          AND      r1,r0,#0x80
000016  b111              CBZ      r1,|L71.30|
000018  f5a07180          SUB      r1,r0,#0x100
00001c  b288              UXTH     r0,r1
                  |L71.30|
;;;35       	if ((savepc>>8) != (PC>>8))   
00001e  1201              ASRS     r1,r0,#8
000020  4a05              LDR      r2,|L71.56|
000022  8812              LDRH     r2,[r2,#0]  ; PC
000024  ebb12f22          CMP      r1,r2,ASR #8
000028  d004              BEQ      |L71.52|
;;;36       		cpu_clockticks++;   
00002a  4905              LDR      r1,|L71.64|
00002c  6809              LDR      r1,[r1,#0]  ; cpu_clockticks
00002e  1c49              ADDS     r1,r1,#1
000030  4a03              LDR      r2,|L71.64|
000032  6011              STR      r1,[r2,#0]  ; cpu_clockticks
                  |L71.52|
;;;37     
;;;38      	return savepc;
;;;39     }   
000034  4770              BX       lr
;;;40     
                          ENDP

000036  0000              DCW      0x0000
                  |L71.56|
                          DCD      ||PC||
                  |L71.60|
                          DCD      operand
                  |L71.64|
                          DCD      cpu_clockticks

                          AREA ||i.cpu_reset||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  cpu_reset PROC
;;;120    /* Reset CPU */   
;;;121    void cpu_reset(void)   
000000  2000              MOVS     r0,#0
;;;122    {   
;;;123    	A=X=Y=0;   
000002  490d              LDR      r1,|L72.56|
000004  7008              STRB     r0,[r1,#0]
000006  490d              LDR      r1,|L72.60|
000008  7008              STRB     r0,[r1,#0]
00000a  490d              LDR      r1,|L72.64|
00000c  7008              STRB     r0,[r1,#0]
;;;124    	P = R_FLAG | Z_FLAG;       //Z_FLAG | R_FLAG   
00000e  2022              MOVS     r0,#0x22
000010  490c              LDR      r1,|L72.68|
000012  7008              STRB     r0,[r1,#0]
;;;125    	S=0xff;   
000014  20ff              MOVS     r0,#0xff
000016  490c              LDR      r1,|L72.72|
000018  7008              STRB     r0,[r1,#0]
;;;126    
;;;127    	PC = RST_VECTOR;

;;;48     };
;;;49     void joypad_write(uint8_t n, uint8_t v) {
000000  b570              PUSH     {r4-r6,lr}
000002  4604              MOV      r4,r0
000004  460d              MOV      r5,r1
;;;50     	// if (joypad_strobe[n] && !v) {
;;;51     	if (v) {
000006  b135              CBZ      r5,|L99.22|

000014  6008              STR      r0,[r1,#0]  ; joypad_state
                  |L99.22|
;;;54     	}
;;;55     	joypad_strobe[n] = v;
000016  4803              LDR      r0,|L99.36|
000018  5505              STRB     r5,[r0,r4]
;;;56     }
00001a  bd70              POP      {r4-r6,pc}
;;;57     
                          ENDP

                  |L99.28|
                          DCD      joypad_read_state
                  |L99.32|
                          DCD      joypad_state
                  |L99.36|
                          DCD      joypad_strobe

                          AREA ||i.sprite_dma||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  sprite_dma PROC
;;;203    
;;;204    void sprite_dma(uint8_t scr_addr)  
000000  b510              PUSH     {r4,lr}
;;;205    {      
;;;206        extern int cpu_clockticks;
;;;207        cpu_clockticks -= 512;
000002  4b1e              LDR      r3,|L100.124|
000004  681b              LDR      r3,[r3,#0]  ; cpu_clockticks
000006  f5a37300          SUB      r3,r3,#0x200
00000a  4c1c              LDR      r4,|L100.124|
00000c  6023              STR      r3,[r4,#0]  ; cpu_clockticks
;;;208    
;;;209        const uint8_t *scr_addrptr = 0;  
00000e  2200              MOVS     r2,#0
;;;210        int     i;   
;;;211    
;;;212        switch(scr_addr >> 4){  
000010  1103              ASRS     r3,r0,#4
000012  2b10              CMP      r3,#0x10
000014  d226              BCS      |L100.100|
000016  e8dff003          TBB      [pc,r3]
00001a  0809              DCB      0x08,0x09
00001c  25252525          DCB      0x25,0x25,0x25,0x25
000020  0d0e0f10          DCB      0x0d,0x0e,0x0f,0x10
000024  11121a1b          DCB      0x11,0x12,0x1a,0x1b
000028  1c1d              DCB      0x1c,0x1d
;;;213        case 0x0: //RAM   
;;;214        case 0x1: 
00002a  bf00              NOP      
;;;215            scr_addrptr = &cpu_ram[(scr_addr << 8)];   
00002c  4b14              LDR      r3,|L100.128|
00002e  eb032200          ADD      r2,r3,r0,LSL #8
;;;216            break;   
000032  e017              B        |L100.100|
;;;217        case 0x6: //SRAM   
;;;218        case 0x7:    
000034  bf00              NOP      
                  |L100.54|
;;;219        #ifdef SRAM 
;;;220            scr_addrptr = SRAM + ((scr_addr << 8) - 0x6000);   
;;;221            break;
;;;222        #else
;;;223            return;
;;;224        #endif   
;;;225        case 0x8:
;;;226        case 0x9:   
;;;227        case 0xA:   
;;;228        case 0xB:   
;;;229            scr_addrptr = &prg_rombank0[(scr_addr << 8) - 0x8000];   
;;;230            break;   
;;;231        case 0xC:   
;;;232        case 0xD:   
;;;233        case 0xE:   
;;;234        case 0xF:   
;;;235            scr_addrptr = &prg_rombank1[(scr_addr << 8) - 0xC000];   
;;;236            break;   
;;;237        }  
;;;238    
;;;239        for(i=0; i<256; i++){   
;;;240            Spr_Mem.spr_ram[i] = scr_addrptr[i];   
;;;241        }   
;;;242    }   
000036  bd10              POP      {r4,pc}
000038  bf00              NOP                            ;226
00003a  bf00              NOP                            ;227
00003c  bf00              NOP                            ;228
00003e  f44f4300          MOV      r3,#0x8000            ;229
000042  ebc32300          RSB      r3,r3,r0,LSL #8       ;229
000046  4c0f              LDR      r4,|L100.132|
000048  6824              LDR      r4,[r4,#0]            ;229  ; prg_rombank0
00004a  191a              ADDS     r2,r3,r4              ;229
00004c  e00a              B        |L100.100|
00004e  bf00              NOP                            ;232
000050  bf00              NOP                            ;233
000052  bf00              NOP                            ;234
000054  f44f4340          MOV      r3,#0xc000            ;235
000058  ebc32300          RSB      r3,r3,r0,LSL #8       ;235
00005c  4c0a              LDR      r4,|L100.136|
00005e  6824              LDR      r4,[r4,#0]            ;235  ; prg_rombank1
000060  191a              ADDS     r2,r3,r4              ;235
000062  bf00              NOP                            ;236
                  |L100.100|
000064  bf00              NOP                            ;216
000066  2100              MOVS     r1,#0                 ;239
000068  e003              B        |L100.114|
                  |L100.106|
00006a  5c53              LDRB     r3,[r2,r1]            ;240
00006c  4c07              LDR      r4,|L100.140|
00006e  5463              STRB     r3,[r4,r1]            ;240
000070  1c49              ADDS     r1,r1,#1              ;239
                  |L100.114|
000072  29ff              CMP      r1,#0xff              ;239
000074  ddf9              BLE      |L100.106|
000076  bf00              NOP      
000078  e7dd              B        |L100.54|
;;;243    
                          ENDP

00007a  0000              DCW      0x0000
